com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/kasabian-tease-announcement-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/kasabian-tease-announcement-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kasabian">Kasabian</a>透露将在下周发布新音乐并发布公告。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-interview-2024-homecoming-leicester-gig-new-album-happenings-glastonbury-killers-3553495">Kasabian 谈话“疯狂”2024 年返校节表演和“迷幻”新专辑“Happenings”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支莱斯特摇滚乐队本周在社交媒体上分享了一段六秒的预告视频，其中有一个电话从“无来电显示”号码响起​​，配乐是强劲的低音吉他线和稳定的军鼓节奏。</p><p>他们在帖子的标题中添加了一系列好奇的眼睛表情符号和日期 21/02，即下周三。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="und" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 21/02 <a href="https://t.co/yRNpfK4UN0">pic.twitter.com/yRNpfK4UN0</a></p><p> - KasabianHQ (@KasabianHQ) <a href="https://twitter.com/KasabianHQ/status/1758175802011574440?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>主唱谢尔盖·皮佐诺 (Serge Pizzorno) 今天（2 月 16 日）还在他的社交媒体上分享了一条以电话为主题的预告片，其中有一个小手机旁边有一个他自己的微型模型，并配文：“我喜欢你打电话的时候。这完全没有意义x。”</p><p>早在 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-announce-new-album-happenings-along-with-huge-summer-solstice-ii-leicester-show-with-kaiser-chiefs-3553082">Kasabian 就宣布了他们的新专辑《Happenings》</a> ，并于今年夏天在家乡莱斯特举办了一场盛大的《夏至 II》演出。</p><p>皮佐诺<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-interview-2024-homecoming-leicester-gig-new-album-happenings-glastonbury-killers-3553495">在接受<em>NME</em>采访时谈到了</a>歌迷对这张唱片的期待，他说：“在 60 年代末，他们会发生一些事情。所以， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hawkwind">Hawkwind</a> ……[伦敦]的圆屋里将会发生一件事情。他们有点迷幻……我想他们是第一批狂欢，你知道吗？他们从 50 年代末开始就得名了。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3aNZqDM-J6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113