//www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-announce-autumn-uk-and-ireland-2024-tour-buy-tickets-3588644">The Libertines 宣布 2024 年秋季英国和爱尔兰巡演的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
